snippet.title: Midnight Acres Gameplay Trailer | Relaxing Farming & Intense FPS
snippet.description:
WISHLIST MIDNIGHT ACRES TODAY -- https://store.steampowered.com/app/2536420/Midnight_Acres/

Experience Midnight Acres — an indie farming sim by day, and intense FPS by night. Unwind and battle on, all in one game as you grow and nurture your farm, plan and upgrade turrets and defenses, and engage in combat with horrifying beasts.
